  <!-- EN: ship shields -->
  <ShipShields.label>飞船护盾</ShipShields.label>
  <!-- EN: Protect your ship with a momentum-repulsor field. -->
  <ShipShields.description>解锁建造可以产生动能排斥场以保护飞船的「护盾发生器」。</ShipShields.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->starship shielding</li>
    <li>subject_story->helped the post-apocalyptic planet Ishwalla return to spaceflight, designing a shield which could survive its orbital debris rings</li>
