  </ShipSpaceSuits.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: EVA powered armor -->
  <ShipSpaceSuitsHeavy.label>重型舱外活动套装</ShipSpaceSuitsHeavy.label>
  <!-- EN: Apply life-support technology to powered armor, producing an armored suit which allows its occupant to survive in outer space. -->
  <ShipSpaceSuitsHeavy.description>解锁建造动力装甲级别的「重型舱外活动套装」。</ShipSpaceSuitsHeavy.description>
