  <!-- EN: ship torpedoes -->
  <ShipTorpedoes.label>飞船鱼雷</ShipTorpedoes.label>
  <!-- EN: Launch powerful torpedoes at enemy ships. Effective at overwhelming shields. -->
  <ShipTorpedoes.description>解锁建造「鱼雷发射管」和制作各种鱼雷，可以有效穿透敌舰护盾并对其造成杀伤。</ShipTorpedoes.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->space torpedoes</li>
    <li>subject_story->took control of a glitterworld antimatter-production facility, diverting its output to manufacture antigrain torpedoes</li>
    <li>subject_story->was rumored to have died by riding a space torpedo while waving a cowboy hat</li>
    <li>subject_story->developed laser-reflective coatings for space torpedoes, improving their ability to survive point defenses</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->launching space torpedoes</li>
  -->
  <ShipTorpedoes.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->太空鱼雷</li>
    <li>subject_story->接管了一座闪耀世界的反物质制造厂，并令其全力装配反粒子鱼雷</li>
    <li>subject_story->听说是因为边骑着太空鱼雷边挥舞着牛仔帽而死的</li>
    <li>subject_story->为太空鱼雷研制了激光反射覆层，提高了它们面对点防御拦截时的生存能力</li>
