  </ShipTorpedoes.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: ship cannons -->
  <ShipTurretAC.label>飞船动能炮塔</ShipTurretAC.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct ballistic slugthrowers for ship-to-ship combat. Unlike energy weapons, these require ammo but need almost no cooling. -->
  <ShipTurretAC.description>解锁建造用于飞船交战的「动能炮塔」，有效射程较近，可切换至点防御模式拦截鱼雷和穿梭机。与其他能量炮塔不同，动能炮塔需要装填实体弹药，但冷却时间很短。</ShipTurretAC.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->starship autocannons</li>
    <li>subject_story->saw energy weapons as needlessly complex, preferring the impact of metal on metal</li>
    <li>subject_story->jury-rigged civilian spacecraft for a desperate assault on a pirate fortress</li>
    <li>subject_story->accidentally ordered more uranium than the ship's reactor could burn, and sought a use for it</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing starship autocannons</li>
  -->
  <ShipTurretAC.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->飞船动能炮塔</li>
    <li>subject_story->觉得能量武器太花里胡哨，更喜欢金属实弹打在金属船体上的那种冲击感</li>
    <li>subject_story->紧急操控民用飞船，对海盗要塞发动了孤注一掷的突击</li>
    <li>subject_story->不小心订购了一大堆飞船反应堆根本用不完的铀，并试着寻找处理它们的办法</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造飞船动能炮塔</li>
  </ShipTurretAC.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: railgun turrets -->
  <ShipTurretKinetic.label>飞船轨道炮塔</ShipTurretKinetic.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct small railguns for ship-to-ship combat. Most effective at long range. -->
