  <!-- EN: capital ship armaments -->
  <ShipTurretLarge.label>主力舰武备</ShipTurretLarge.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct modular spinal-mount weapons, typically seen only on capital ships. -->
  <ShipTurretLarge.description>解锁建造模块化的脊峰火炮。这种威力惊人的武器通常只在主力舰上配备。</ShipTurretLarge.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->spinal weaponry</li>
    <li>subject_story->fought in the last stand of Old Ishwalla, desperately firing asteroid-based weapons against an endless horde of mechanoid dropships</li>
    <li>subject_story->served aboard the KSS Judgement, an archotech-built starship whose primary gun was rumored to be kilometers long</li>
