  </ShipTurretLarge.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: laser turrets -->
  <ShipTurretLaser.label>飞船激光炮塔</ShipTurretLaser.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct small lasers for ship-to-ship combat. Highly damaging but only usable at short range. Can intercept torpedoes. -->
  <ShipTurretLaser.description>解锁建造用于飞船交战的「激光炮塔」，有效射程较近，可切换至点防御模式拦截鱼雷和穿梭机。</ShipTurretLaser.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->starship lasers</li>
    <li>subject_story->sacrificed one eye to an archotech in exchange for the secrets of laser weaponry (later losing the other eye to laser backscatter)</li>
